		<title>Nvidia GTX 1070 Ti review: A fine graphics card—but price remains high</title>
		<link>https://arstechnica.com/?p=1196745</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 13:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Mark Walton]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Gaming & Culture]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Tech]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[AMD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Gadgetology]]></category>
